package-lookup - Look up package information

USAGE:
    package-lookup <package-name>

DESCRIPTION:
    Look up information about a package including
    installation status and available versions.

ARGUMENTS:
    package-name
        Name of the package to look up (required)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-install-app-registry-git-url URL
        Git URL for app registry (default: https://github.com/walterjwhite/app.registry.git)

    -conf-install-app-registry-timeout SECONDS
        App registry timeout (default: 5)

EXAMPLES:
    package-lookup my-package
